<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Received | Diet Plan</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-6">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full bg-white rounded-2xl p-10 text-center">
        <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-green-50 rounded-full">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Thanks for Applying, <%= name %>!</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-base leading-relaxed">
            I've received your details and I'm already looking into them. I will work on your personalized diet plan
            over the next 24 hours and get back to you with a detailed strategy via WhatsApp.
        </p>
        <a href="/"
            class="inline-block w-full py-4 bg-black text-white rounded-xl font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
            Apply for another plan
        </a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>